snippet.title: Glass Animals - Heat Waves / Japanese Cover

i've had this song stuck in my head for quite a while now,
i hope you like this one as much as i do! : )

special thanks to my friend, ERA, for the rearrangement!
he did a really good job turning this into a chill cover. 🔥🌊
